Sentencas: Layered perovskite oxides have attracted great attention in the electrochemical-energy field due to fast oxygen kinetics at low temperature and high electronic/ionic conductivity.
Titulo: Evaluation of calcium codoping in double perovskite PrBaCo2O5+δ as cathode material for IT-SOFCs

Sentencas: Developing low-cost, high-performance electrocatalysts is a necessary path for the commercialization of electrochemical energy devices.
Titulo: Evaluation of calcium codoping in double perovskite PrBaCo2O5+δ as cathode material for IT-SOFCs

Sentencas: In the current research study, PrBaCo2O5+delta codoping with Ca to substitute Pr and Ba is prepared by a modified complexing sol-gel process.
Titulo: Evaluation of calcium codoping in double perovskite PrBaCo2O5+δ as cathode material for IT-SOFCs

Sentencas: New perovskite oxides Pr0.9Ca0.1Ba1-xCaxCo2O5+delta (x = 0-0.2, PCBCx) remained in a pure-phase tetragonal (P4/mmm) structure.
Titulo: Evaluation of calcium codoping in double perovskite PrBaCo2O5+δ as cathode material for IT-SOFCs

Sentencas: PCBCx exhibit good chemical compatibility with Ce0.8Sm0.2O1.9 (SDC) after calcining at 1000 degrees C for 10 h. The doping of calcium ions at the Ba-site effectively improved the electrical conductivity.
Titulo: Evaluation of calcium codoping in double perovskite PrBaCo2O5+δ as cathode material for IT-SOFCs

Sentencas: XPS analysis indicate that Co ions exist at +3 and +4 valence states in PCBCx samples.
Titulo: Evaluation of calcium codoping in double perovskite PrBaCo2O5+δ as cathode material for IT-SOFCs

Sentencas: The thermal-expansion coefficients (TECs) of PCBCx samples decrease as the calcium ion doping concentration increasing.
Titulo: Evaluation of calcium codoping in double perovskite PrBaCo2O5+δ as cathode material for IT-SOFCs

Sentencas: The polarization resistance of a PCBCx cathode on the SDC electrolyte, where x = 0-0.3 at 700 degrees C, are 0.097, 0.076, 0.069, and 0.106 Omega cm(2), respectively.
Titulo: Evaluation of calcium codoping in double perovskite PrBaCo2O5+δ as cathode material for IT-SOFCs

Sentencas: The x = 0.2 cathode reveals the best electrochemical performance.
Titulo: Evaluation of calcium codoping in double perovskite PrBaCo2O5+δ as cathode material for IT-SOFCs

Sentencas: The maximum power densities of the PCBC2 cathode are 712, 541, and 392 mW cm(-2) at 800, 750, and 700 degrees C, respectively.
Titulo: Evaluation of calcium codoping in double perovskite PrBaCo2O5+δ as cathode material for IT-SOFCs
